					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Also, if this wasn't clear, it is safe to write $4012/4013 when the $4015 bit is clear as well. The one thing you should probably do is clear the loop flag if it's being used before setting $4012/4013, so you don't have a chance of reloading the loop to the wrong sample... but since you're probably about to restart it again within a few cycles, even if you forgot to do this the difference would be negligible.</div>

